Package hospital

Class Room

java.lang.Object
hospital.Room
public class Room extends Object
The Room class represents a room in the hospital. It contains the room's id, name, type, capacity, current occupation, occupied status and access. The access is a list of functions that have access to the room. The room can be occupied or not. The room can be accessed by different functions. The room can be revoked access to a function. The room can be printed. The room can be incremented or decremented in occupation.
